  "title": "Finance & Admin Officer (AR)",
  "description": "<p><strong>KEY RESPONSIBILITIES AND ACCOUNTABILITES</strong></p><ul><li>Monthly invoicing of nursing home fees and other charges to residents.</li><li>Collection of payments from residents.</li><li>Track residents’ insurance payouts eg: IDAPE and Eldershield.</li><li>Update transactions into accounting software.</li><li>Generate Statement of Account to residents and follow up with outstanding receivables.</li><li>Handle all other administrative matters pertaining to residents and next of kin at the Home.</li><li>General administrative duties (eg: attend to walk in and call in enquiries) and any other ad-hoc duties.</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Attained at least LCCI accounting qualification</li><li>Minimum 2 years of working experience</li><li>Pleasant personality and good team-spirit</li><li>Able to communicate well with people from various walks of life</li><li>Able to speak Mandarin and/or dialects is advantageous as need to liaise with Mandarin/dialect speaking clients</li></ul>",
